name: WAS £59 - 'I HAVE BUTTERFLIES' Silver, amethyst & aquamarine bracelet/necklace
description:
Combining butterfly beads and charms with beautiful gemstones that represent feelings of calm and reassurance, these hand crafted pieces make an ideal gift for a loved one who may be facing an important event in their life, or a treat for oneself - everyone needs a bit of calm and reassurance at times.

This piece can be worn as a necklace or wrapped around your wrist as a bracelet.

AQUAMARINE: A stone of courage that helps to calm nerves, releases anxiety and removes fear.

AMETHYST: Is said to impart a calming influence and can help overcome fears.

*Each piece comes in a beautiful custom made pouch, with a label attached explaining the different gemstone meanings
